hob ikh nisht batsolt farn kumen aher.

419
00:20:22,297 --> 00:20:23,675
un nokh dem,

420
00:20:24,204 --> 00:20:25,855
ho'mir gekumen aher,

421
00:20:25,855 --> 00:20:27,253
gelign gelt

422
00:20:27,478 --> 00:20:32,664
bay der mishpokhe. nisht in keyn bank, vayl fun vu zol ikh nemen, in bank broykh men tsoln,

423
00:20:32,664 --> 00:20:34,681
ir veyst a- a- a-

424
00:20:34,717 --> 00:20:37,743
hob ikh es ikh, un ven nisht broykh ikh nisht un ikh hob,

425
00:20:37,743 --> 00:20:39,507
ikh hob keyn mol nisht getun azoy.

426
00:20:39,507 --> 00:20:41,549
se geven do a kleyn gevelbl,

427
00:20:41,552 --> 00:20:44,502
er hot gevoynt a shokhn tir un tir bayn undz,

428
00:20:44,502 --> 00:20:49,353
un er hot gehat do a gevelb. hot er mir gezogt, "Riki, vos du broykhst, kum un nem

429
00:20:49,353 --> 00:20:53,713
un loz nisht di kinder zoln zey hungern." zog ikh, yo yo, ikh vel shoyn kumen.

430
00:20:53,853 --> 00:21:00,896
gring tsu nemen un tsu esn un nokh dem vi zol ikh tsoln? ikh hob nisht gehat. undz zenen geven oyf groyse gehakte tsores.

431
00:21:00,924 --> 00:21:02,420
ober se hot zikh,

432
00:21:03,303 --> 00:21:11,249
mayn zun hot ongehoybn helfn farn SOKHNUT dort oder der deys farrikhtn un yents farrikhtn, er hot nebekh gevolt fardinen, er iz geven a yung kind

433
00:21:11,252 --> 00:21:14,081
un er hot ongehoybn geyn arbetn keyn Tel Aviv,

434
00:21:14,424 --> 00:21:19,416
se se mir geven mit khreyn. un dos meydl iz gegangen keyn Yerusholaim lernen,

435
00:21:19,453 --> 00:21:24,594
un zi hot gut gelernt borekhashem, un un un er hot oysgelernt a gut fakh

436
00:21:25,258 --> 00:21:28,948
un deys hot zikh oyfge-.

437
00:21:28,059 --> 00:21:30,197
der man, vos iz geshen mitn man?

438
00:21:29,763 --> 00:21:31,614
er iz bald krank gevorn.

439
00:21:31,637 --> 00:21:34,450
fun o- galykh nokh, kurtse tsayt nokhn onkumen?

440
00:21:32,902 --> 00:21:35,220
n- n- nisht keyn sakh,

441
00:21:35,220 --> 00:21:36,407
nisht keyn sakh.

442
00:21:36,041 --> 00:21:37,824
iz er geven ale yorn krank?

443
00:21:37,408 --> 00:21:38,870
ale yorn krank.

444
00:21:38,640 --> 00:21:41,520
ir, bay vos hot ir, ir hot oykh gearbet?

445
00:21:40,631 --> 00:21:42,667
ikh, azoy vi a ferd.

446
00:21:42,183 --> 00:21:43,899
bay vos hot ir gearbet.

447
00:21:43,868 --> 00:21:46,953
ikh bin gegan arbetn tsu der troybn,

448
00:21:47,094 --> 00:21:51,257
shnaydn troybn hob ikh a mol gesh- ikh hob UNK gezen vi azoy se vakst troybn.

449
00:21:52,224 --> 00:21:54,744
kumt der balbos un zogt azoy,

450
00:21:54,744 --> 00:21:57,230
"ver redt, rirtst mit di fingerlekh."

451
00:21:57,962 --> 00:22:00,993
nu, rir mit di fingerlekh, rir ikh.

452
00:22:02,079 --> 00:22:05,510
hots zikh dort oyfgehert, bin ikh gegan oyf an ander plats.

453
00:22:05,538 --> 00:22:10,193
a klal, yener iz geven an aynshtendiker mentsh. in a tog zog ikh tsun im azoy.

454
00:22:10,193 --> 00:22:15,399
"du lo'mikh nemen tsvey shtrenglekh troybn, az ikh vel mir trogn di kinder aheym, zenen nebekh hungerik.

455
00:22:15,399 --> 00:22:17,399
a shtikl broyt vel ikh zey nokh gebn."

456
00:22:17,399 --> 00:22:23,912
dos harts hot mir gerisn. zey zenen geven beyde azolkhe sheyne kinder. me hot mir gezogt, do, ven ikh bin gekumen,

457
00:22:23,912 --> 00:22:26,170
zolst visn me vet zikh undzer farlibn.

458
00:22:26,565 --> 00:22:27,758
azoy iz geven.

459
00:22:28,117 --> 00:22:29,816
in beyde hot men zikh farlibt.

460
00:22:30,868 --> 00:22:33,731
iz hot ir gearbet bay troybn, un bay vos nokh?

461
00:22:32,319 --> 00:22:34,122
hob ikh gearbet bay di tro-

462
00:22:34,122 --> 00:22:36,128
un oyfn felt mit vate.

463
00:22:36,369 --> 00:22:39,007
dort iz shoyn geven a pakhed oyf der velt.

464
00:22:39,007 --> 00:22:40,532
di nase vate.

465
00:22:41,195 --> 00:22:43,412
ongebundn a a zak do,

466
00:22:43,423 --> 00:22:48,902
un ikh hob geshnitn gikh, geshikt, di hent zenen gegangen, mit a shokhnte beyde,

467
00:22:49,127 --> 00:22:53,537
un ikh hob gebroykht visn velkhe rey ikh gey tsurik, vayl ikh bin gegan UNK.

468
00:22:53,537 --> 00:22:59,114
der balbos funem kibuts zogt azoy, "GVERET, ven zen ir gekumen, vos ir zent azoy geshikt?"

469
00:22:59,114 --> 00:23:02,503
zog ikh, "di tsores traybn mikh, vayl ikh hob nisht vos tsu esn."

470
00:23:02,593 --> 00:23:05,762
ah hot er mikh ongekukt, der kibutsnik,

471
00:23:05,762 --> 00:23:08,243
nu, ikh hob gearbet epes a zibn teg,

472
00:23:08,243 --> 00:23:10,234
hot mikh ongehoybn vey tun der kreyts,

473
00:23:10,234 --> 00:23:11,677
trogndik dey dos.

474
00:23:11,677 --> 00:23:14,349
gegesn hob ikh gornisht,

475
00:23:14,625 --> 00:23:20,140
zeyer shver. ikh hob azoy fil hunger gelitn az der fun oybn zol ophitn.

476
00:23:20,143 --> 00:23:21,625
vifl ikh hob gelitn.

477
00:23:21,625 --> 00:23:23,136
un nebekh, er,

478
00:23:23,147 --> 00:23:25,521
vos ikh hob gekent hob ikh in im geshtupt.

479
00:23:26,589 --> 00:23:30,751
un dort hot zikh geendikt,

480
00:23:31,095 --> 00:23:33,151
bin ikh gekumen tsu der LISHKA,

481
00:23:33,170 --> 00:23:38,179
zogt men mir, ikh ken aykh vayter gebn ergetser oyfn feld. zog ikh, geb mir shoyn nisht oyfn feld,

482
00:23:38,179 --> 00:23:40,584
ikh hob mir shoyn aroysgenumen mayn kheylek.

483
00:23:40,584 --> 00:23:47,491
a- er kukt mikh on vi azoy ikh kuk oys, shvarts bin ikh geven vi a koyl, fun deye vos zenen gekumen mit mir,

484
00:23:47,767 --> 00:23:50,360
fun fun Yevno,

485
00:23:50,771 --> 00:23:52,278
fun Rumenye,

486
00:23:52,278 --> 00:23:59,050
zey hobn mikh nisht derkent ven zey zenen gekumen do. shpeter mit mit tsvey vokhn hobn hobn zey mir, "Riki iz shoyn farshvartst gevorn."

487
00:23:59,546 --> 00:24:01,282
hobn dokh gekumen in a dire,

488
00:24:01,282 --> 00:24:03,034
se hot nisht oysgezen azoy.

489
00:24:03,832 --> 00:24:06,049
do iz geven a kokh, vu ikh zits.

490
00:24:06,060 --> 00:24:09,508
ikh hob shoyn ariber gemakht, ikh hob nisht gehat vu tsu leygn di tokhter.

491
00:24:09,508 --> 00:24:12,618
se iz geven shverikeytn, ober ikh hob shtark shver gearbet.

492
00:24:11,696 --> 00:24:13,918
bay vos hot ir UNK shpeter gearbet?

493
00:24:13,468 --> 00:24:15,420
bin ikh arayn in Shefa Hon.

494
00:24:15,662 --> 00:24:16,736
Shefa Hon.

495
00:24:16,860 --> 00:24:23,430
oybn, in der fabrik. nu, dort hob ikh mikh mekhaye geven, vayl se gevezn unter a dakh,

496
00:24:16,978 --> 00:24:17,968
fabrik.

497
00:24:23,430 --> 00:24:25,024
un shoyn nisht oyf der zun.

498
00:24:25,061 --> 00:24:28,920
iz geven a MENAHEL, er heyst Rout,

499
00:24:29,364 --> 00:24:31,232
a, er iz a tshekhisher.

500
00:24:32,233 --> 00:24:39,973
eyn mol shtelt er mikh do un eyn mol shtelt er mikh dort, ober vu er hot mikh geshtelt bin ikh geven fayer in ale zaytn, nisht vayl ikh zol aykh zogn, nor

501
00:24:40,113 --> 00:24:43,162
er hot azoy gehat UNK vi emes ikh dertseyl aykh.

502
00:24:43,522 --> 00:24:48,219
"du rumenisher kop!" vos epes hot er mir geshrign rumenisher kop?

503
00:24:48,219 --> 00:24:51,426
zog ikh den, "azoy vi du bist aza goylem, a tshekhisher,

504
00:24:51,426 --> 00:24:52,764
vos konstu?"

505
00:24:52,888 --> 00:24:56,707
ikh hob im geentfert. meyle, se do iz men dokh UNK.

506
00:24:56,718 --> 00:24:58,164
oyf dem aroyf

507
00:24:58,389 --> 00:25:00,774
iz dos mashindl,

508
00:25:00,774 --> 00:25:02,942
me hot, dort hob ikh gemakht azoy,

509
00:25:02,979 --> 00:25:05,319
un se geven a tishl,

510
00:25:05,426 --> 00:25:07,752
in eyn zayt a benkl

511
00:25:07,752 --> 00:25:12,586
un a groyse kastn, vos me fleg alts araynshikn fun UNK in dem,

512
00:25:12,586 --> 00:25:18,717
un me hot gebroykht onfiln zeklekh vegn un zey tsamleygn dort, un eyner hot gebroykht zey tsumakhn.

513
00:25:19,550 --> 00:25:22,728
iz geven eyner der zayt un eyner der.

514
00:25:22,728 --> 00:25:28,542
n- iz geven mayne a shokhnte di eyne, un ikh bin geven di tsveyte, un ikh hob gezen vi azoy deye

515
00:25:29,453 --> 00:25:31,588
⟨Morokoriso⟩

516
00:25:31,588 --> 00:25:32,693
der Anita,

517
00:25:32,693 --> 00:25:36,301
vos dey hot gearbet bay di mashin vos hot tsugemakht.

518
00:25:36,594 --> 00:25:38,827
in a tog kum ikh arayn,

519
00:25:38,827 --> 00:25:40,925
zogt der MENAHEL azoy:

520
00:25:41,235 --> 00:25:42,565
"Regina!

521
00:25:42,565 --> 00:25:46,039
du muzt zikh dikh oyslernen oyf der mashindl arbetn!"

522
00:25:46,247 --> 00:25:48,638
zog ikh, "nu, vos iz aza groyse zakh?"

523
00:25:50,347 --> 00:25:52,974
punkt iz gevezn KEMAKH TIRAS,

524
00:25:53,722 --> 00:25:56,960
ts- dos iz azolkhe hoykhe peklekh, shver,

525
00:25:56,960 --> 00:25:59,421
se shver arunter tsu rukn.

526
00:25:59,831 --> 00:26:01,935
der hot zikh aropgezetst,

527
00:26:02,160 --> 00:26:10,676
un er hot ongehoybn tsu ⟨shurkn⟩ mit di drayers aruntergegangen unter dem. er hot geleygt un geleygt un geleygt, efsher leygt er ir nokh.

528
00:26:10,867 --> 00:26:13,151
zog ikh, nu, veystu vos, heyb zikh shoyn oyf!

529
00:26:13,162 --> 00:26:16,903
nu, du vest shoyn visn dem ⟨aleyner kop⟩. zog ikh, e'mir zen.

530
00:26:17,280 --> 00:26:22,517
ikh hob mikh aropgezetst teykef, ikh hob a nem geton deys, se gehat aza kleyn bretele

531
00:26:22,517 --> 00:26:24,213
farn mashindl.

532
00:26:24,213 --> 00:26:26,423
ikh hob a shokl geton mit dem,

533
00:26:26,423 --> 00:26:29,205
hot zikh a bisele gezetst un a ruk arunter,

534
00:26:29,362 --> 00:26:32,954
"kuk on vos far a hent du host! du host a gezuntn kop oyf zikh."

535
00:26:32,954 --> 00:26:33,755
zog ikh, "vos den?

536
00:26:33,755 --> 00:26:35,949
ikh es mir ⟨aleyn⟩ broyt, ober du,

537
00:26:35,949 --> 00:26:39,299
vos kenstu, du tshekhisher goylem?" ikh hob im gezogt.

538
00:26:39,318 --> 00:26:40,843
aroyf un arop,

539
00:26:40,888 --> 00:26:44,631
ikh hob gearbet dort etlekhe teg, bay di dem tishl,

540
00:26:44,651 --> 00:26:45,543
far vos

541
00:26:45,543 --> 00:26:49,736
yener hot nisht, me hot es oyf der nakht ibergemakht, zi hot gemakht di zeklekh,

542
00:26:49,736 --> 00:26:51,946
fun eyn zayt zi hot zey gebroykht tsumakhn.

543
00:26:51,946 --> 00:26:53,862
hot men dokh gebroykht deys mashindl.

544
00:26:53,862 --> 00:26:56,343
nu, oyf in der fri bin ikh gegangen tsu dem.

545
00:26:56,343 --> 00:26:57,504
in a tog

546
00:26:58,404 --> 00:27:00,519
shtelt zikh arop der MENAHEL

547
00:27:00,519 --> 00:27:02,398
fun der fabrik.

548
00:27:04,125 --> 00:27:05,959
shtelt zikh azoy dort,

549
00:27:06,167 --> 00:27:08,197
un er shteyt

550
00:27:08,242 --> 00:27:12,222
mit eyn hant in tash un mit eyn hant mitn tsigarye.

551
00:27:12,222 --> 00:27:16,016
un nemt nisht arop di oygn az vos ikh tu.

552
00:27:17,760 --> 00:27:23,571
ikh ken mikh nisht oyfhoybn un un ikh trayb nebekh dey tsvey vos zey broykhn dos vegn un zey shrayen gevald.

553
00:27:23,582 --> 00:27:29,097
makh a bisele shtayter, makh a bi- zog ikh, kuk, ikh ken mikh nisht rirn; kuk vi azoy der shteyt do iber mir.

554
00:27:29,705 --> 00:27:34,292
un ikh hob gearbet un aropgevorfn oyfn, se geven oyf der erd vu tsu varfn.

555
00:27:35,343 --> 00:27:36,485
alzo,

556
00:27:37,180 --> 00:27:39,371
se iz etlekhe teg azoy.

557
00:27:39,680 --> 00:27:42,054
ikh kum aheym nebekh, mayn man fregt,

558
00:27:42,279 --> 00:27:44,805
Riki, host shoyn bakumen a por funt?

559
00:27:46,076 --> 00:27:47,927
zog ikh, neyn, nokh nisht.

560
00:27:49,367 --> 00:27:51,943
nu, vos kon er nebekh tun?

561
00:27:52,353 --> 00:27:55,385
eyn mol un tsvey mol. in a sheynem tog,

562
00:27:55,914 --> 00:27:58,645
hot men im shoyn gegebn der der

563
00:27:58,645 --> 00:27:59,523
et men.

564
00:27:59,523 --> 00:28:02,271
zogt der MENAHEL, geyts arayn, me gebt gelt.

565
00:28:02,563 --> 00:28:05,454
der der, nisht der MENAHEL, der balbos.

566
00:28:05,454 --> 00:28:07,251
ikh gey arayn der br- der,

567
00:28:07,271 --> 00:28:08,770
in MISRAD,

568
00:28:08,770 --> 00:28:13,251
ikh hob nisht gevust der balbos mitn, mit der yener zenen zikh man un vayb,

569
00:28:13,262 --> 00:28:15,183
vos veys ikh ver di zenen?

570
00:28:15,183 --> 00:28:17,019
zey hobn zikh mir nisht forgeshtelt.

571
00:28:17,463 --> 00:28:20,574
 iz gegangen der dos,

572
00:28:20,602 --> 00:28:27,836
un zi nemt un zi tseylt un tseylt un tseylt, zog ikh, reboyne-sheloylem, az zi vet mir dos gebn bin ikh a negideste.

573
00:28:28,635 --> 00:28:30,570
ober ikh vel es nisht tsunemen.

574
00:28:30,727 --> 00:28:35,632
vayl ikh vil vayter arbetn, un zi vet zikh nokh dem derkenen az zi hot nisht gut gegebn.

575
00:28:36,228 --> 00:28:37,387
zog ikh ir,

576
00:28:37,798 --> 00:28:39,615
do hot ir, deys iz ayer.

577
00:28:40,076 --> 00:28:44,222
ikh nem dos gelt in di hent, zog ikh, ober ir veyst ir hot zaykh toye gevezn?

578
00:28:44,548 --> 00:28:46,486
zogt zi, neyn, ikh nisht.

579
00:28:46,486 --> 00:28:50,148
mayn man hot gezogt, ir arbet epes azoyns un azelekhs.

580
00:28:50,148 --> 00:28:54,431
nor ikh bin aheymgekumen mit epes a draysik oder fertsik funt tsurik,

581
00:28:55,297 --> 00:29:00,320
un az ikh hob a shtel geton dos berzele nebekh far mayn man, un er hot gezen,

582
00:29:01,153 --> 00:29:02,272
"Riki!

583
00:29:02,272 --> 00:29:06,143
host dikh epes zeyer a sakh bakumen." zog ikh, vayl di hent arbetn.

584
00:29:08,055 --> 00:29:12,151
do veln mir vayter oyfhern un aribergeyn tsu der nekster kasete, mit ayer erloybenish.

